{"tid":1559457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵公開8‧31截圖 無速龍或防暴警在月台或車廂行動及拘捕人的關鍵畫面","createTime":"2019-09-10T23:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T02:01:06.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ac581948e960da02fbcecaae53ce66017356a9","tid":1559457,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:02:10.000Z","msg":"港鐵公開8‧31截圖 無速龍用武畫面 拒公開閉路電視片段 無諮詢私隱署<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】8．31太子站事件，警方被質疑於港鐵車廂打人使用過度武力，其間傳媒被拒入月台採訪，「打死人」等謠言四起。事隔10日，港鐵首度公開太子、荔枝角及油麻地站共21張閉路電視片段截圖重組時序，但無速龍小隊或防暴警在月台或車廂行動及拘捕人的關鍵畫面。港鐵承認站內3部閉路電視損毁，並續以私隱為由拒公開片段。有議員認為公眾知情權更重要，當晚目擊者亦稱截圖不能釋除對警方濫權的疑慮，必須公開片段。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190911/s00001/1568140464661/%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e5%85%ac%e9%96%8b8-31%e6%88%aa%e5%9c%96-%e7%84%a1%e9%80%9f%e9%be%8d%e7%94%a8%e6%ad%a6%e7%95%ab%e9%9d%a2-%e6%8b%92%e5%85%ac%e9%96%8b%e9%96%89%e8%b7%af%e9%9b%bb%e8%a6%96%e7%89%87%e6%ae%b5-%e7%84%a1%e8%ab%ae%e8%a9%a2%e7%a7%81%e9%9a%b1%e7%bd%b2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568140464661%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e5%2585%25ac%25e9%2596%258b8-31%25e6%2588%25aa%25e5%259c%2596-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e9%2580%259f%25e9%25be%258d%25e7%2594%25a8%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e7%2595%25ab%25e9%259d%25a2-%25e6%258b%2592%25e5%2585%25ac%25e9%2596%258b%25e9%2596%2589%25e8%25b7%25af%25e9%259b%25bb%25e8%25a6%2596%25e7%2589%2587%25e6%25ae%25b5-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e8%25ab%25ae%25e8%25a9%25a2%25e7%25a7%2581%25e9%259a%25b1%25e7%25bd%25b2&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=af649e03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190911%2Fs00001%2F1568140464661%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e5%2585%25ac%25e9%2596%258b8-31%25e6%2588%25aa%25e5%259c%2596-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e9%2580%259f%25e9%25be%258d%25e7%2594%25a8%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e7%2595%25ab%25e9%259d%